Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_uart::_sfe

The shadow FIFO enable register is a shadow register for MIO_UART(0..1)_FCR[EN] that can be used to remove the burden of having to store the previously written value to MIO_UART(0..1)_FCR in memory and having to mask this value so that only the FIFO enable bit gets updated.
